OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1779894668
OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,FMLAs have spent several hours debating
OL,7,Fa proposal which could see fox hunting
OL,8,Fbanned in Northern Ireland.
OL,10,FStormont heard a fresh bid to outlaw
OL,11,Fhunting is both "balanced" and will
OL,12,Fbring NI "into line with the rest of
OL,13,Fthe UK".
OL,15,FAlliance MLA John Blair previously
OL,16,Fproposed a Private Member's Bill to
OL,17,Fban hunting wild mammals with dogs,
OL,18,Fbut in 2021 the Northern Ireland
OL,19,FAssembly voted by 45 votes to 38 to
OL,20,Freject it.
OL,26,@sD@QOUsD@ZO]tD@JOUuD@GO]
