OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1779894668
OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,FHe relaunched this bid in April,
OL,7,Fintroducing another Private Member's
OL,8,FBill which also proposes prohibiting
OL,9,Ftrail hunting.
OL,11,FOn Tuesday, the Bill reached its
OL,12,Fsecond stage in the Assembly.
OL,14,FMr Blair opened the debate by pointing
OL,15,Fout that Northern Ireland is currently
OL,16,Fthe only part of the United Kingdom
OL,17,Fwithout such a ban.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1779894668
OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,F"England and Wales banned hunting with
OL,7,Fdogs more than 20 years ago, Scotland
OL,8,Fnot only introduced a ban but in fact
OL,9,Fstrengthened its legislation in 2023
OL,10,Fthrough the Hunting with Dogs
OL,11,F(Scotland) Act, creating the most
OL,12,Frobust framework anywhere in the UK,"
OL,13,Fhe told MLAs.
OL,15,F"Yet here in Northern Ireland wild
OL,16,Fmammals can still be chased,
OL,17,Fexhausted, attacked and killed by
OL,18,Fpacks of dogs for sport.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@eO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1779894668
OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,F"The terms of this Bill have been
OL,7,Ftried and tested in the rest of the
OL,8,FUK, the only people who need to worry
OL,9,Fabout it are those who enjoy the
OL,10,Fcruelty of encouraging dogs to chase a
OL,11,Fwild mammal for the kill."
OL,13,FReferring to his previous bid, Mr
OL,14,FBlair said this Bill "reflects changes
OL,15,Fmade after engagement, consultation
OL,16,Fand further consideration".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@ZO]vD@VOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1779894668
OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,F"But what has not changed is the
OL,7,Fcentral fact at the heart of this
OL,8,Fdebate, hunting wild mammals with dogs
OL,9,Fis cruel, unnecessary and a ban is
OL,10,Flong overdue," he added.
OL,12,FHe closed his speech by describing his
OL,13,FBill as taking a "balanced approach,
OL,14,Ftargeting cruelty while preserving
OL,15,Flegitimate exemptions for lawful land
OL,16,Fmanagement".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]uD@ROUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
