PN,44506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1779894668
OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,F"It closes loopholes that have caused
OL,7,Fdifficulty elsewhere, it aligns
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland with the direction of
OL,9,Ftravel across the UK and it responds
OL,10,Fto clear public demand for change," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"It is time to stop allowing wild
OL,14,Fmammals to be chased and killed by
OL,15,Fpacks of dogs in Northern Ireland.
OL,16,FBloodsports have no place in a modern
OL,17,Fcivilised society."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@cO]uD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
