OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,FRobbie Butler, chairman of the
OL,7,FAgriculture, Environment and Rural
OL,8,FAffairs Committee, said at a meeting
OL,9,Fin April that members of the committee
OL,10,Fdid not take a position on the general
OL,11,Fprinciples of the Bill, but agreed to
OL,12,Fconsider the matter further within
OL,13,Ftheir respective parties.
OL,15,FThe UUP representative said his party
OL,16,Fis "broadly supportive of the
OL,17,Fprinciples underpinning the Hunting
OL,18,Fwith Dogs Bill", but that that support
OL,19,Fis "qualified by the need for robust
OL,20,Fscrutiny and clear legal certainty".
OL,26,@xD@DOUzD@OO]{D@DOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
