PN,44508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1779894668
OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,F"We believe that there are legitimate
OL,7,Fquestions which must be addressed to
OL,8,Fensure that the lawful rural
OL,9,Factivities, responsible dog ownership
OL,10,Fand those who hunt for food are not
OL,11,Funintentionally captured by overly
OL,12,Fbroad drafting," he added.
OL,14,FDuring the debate, Sinn Fein MLA Aine
OL,15,FMurphy indicated her party will back
OL,16,Fthe Bill progressing to committee
OL,17,Fstage.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@PO]vD@Zrr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
