CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1779894668
OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the DUP's Tom Buchanan said
OL,7,Fhe opposed the Bill, contending it is
OL,8,F"legislatively weak, practically
OL,9,Funworkable and fundamentally damaging
OL,10,Fto the rural people of Northern
OL,11,FIreland".
OL,13,F"This House has a duty to pass laws
OL,14,Fthat are clear, that are
OL,15,Fproportionate, that are enforceable
OL,16,Fand grounded in evidence, and this
OL,17,FBill before the House today fails to
OL,18,Fmeet each one of these tests," he said.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@HO]uD@AOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
