OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,FEarlier, members of Countryside
OL,7,FAlliance Ireland staged a
OL,8,Fdemonstration with dogs outside
OL,9,FParliament Buildings in opposition to
OL,10,Fthe Bill.
OL,12,FDirector Gary McCartney claimed it is
OL,13,Fa "full-scale attack on not only
OL,14,Fhunting, but every aspect of rural
OL,15,Flife".
OL,26,@uD@COUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
