CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1779894668
OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,F"John Blair's unjustified and
OL,7,Findiscriminate Bill has wide-ranging
OL,8,Fconsequences and will dangerously
OL,9,Fimpact all aspects of country life:
OL,10,Ffrom the mere act of walking a dog, to
OL,11,Ffield sports and vital wildlife
OL,12,Fmanagement," he said.
OL,14,F"He is opting for a culture war
OL,15,Fagainst rural people with a full-scale
OL,16,Fattack on not only hunting, but every
OL,17,Faspect of rural life.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@LO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
