PN,44512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1779894668
OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,F"At a time when people are suffering
OL,7,Ffrom the cost-of-living crisis and
OL,8,Fspiralling energy bills, it defies all
OL,9,Flogic that any politician should deem
OL,10,Fthis a priority for Northern Ireland.
OL,12,F"MLAs need to seriously consider
OL,13,Fwhether they will support this
OL,14,Funjustified and fundamentally flawed
OL,15,FBill that will have devastating
OL,16,Feffects on anyone in the countryside
OL,17,Fwith dogs. We will be fighting this
OL,18,Fappalling piece of legislation to the
OL,19,Fvery end."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
