OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,FThe League Against Cruel Sports also
OL,7,Fattended at Stormont on Tuesday.
OL,9,FRobbie Marsland, director for the
OL,10,Forganisation in Northern Ireland and
OL,11,FScotland, said it supports the Bill,
OL,12,Fwhich he said will bring NI into line
OL,13,Fwith the rest of the United Kingdom
OL,14,Fand "make sure that the cruel and
OL,15,Funnecessary pursuit of hunting with
OL,16,Fdogs is over for good".
OL,26,@vD@EOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
