OL,3,CFresh proposal to end hunting with
OL,4,Cdogs in NI is 'balanced', MLA says
OL,6,F"The idea of encouraging a pack of
OL,7,Fhounds to chase and kill a wild animal
OL,8,Fis repugnant to 76-77% of the Northern
OL,9,FIreland, and that goes across town and
OL,10,Fcountry," he said.
